headline: FTAI Unit To Pursue AI Data Center Power Market; Stock Breaks Out
summary: FTAI Aviation stock soared after the company announced plans for a new business unit dedicated to converting jet engines into power turbines that would supply energy to data centers.

headline: Ukraine Ditches NATO Membership Bid: A Defense ETF Buying Opportunity?
